collectors.title: Database
collectors.titleDetails: (3 total Queries, 3 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT SUM(tbl_orders.quantity) as quantity, MAX(tbl_orders.orderCode) as orderCode, MAX(tbl_orders.order_date) as order_date, MAX(tbl_orders.amount_paid) as amount_paid, SUM(tbl_orders.total_amount) as total_amount, MAX(tbl_orders.change_amount) as change_amount FROM `tbl_orders` JOIN `product_tbl` ON `product_tbl`.`prod_id` = `tbl_orders`.`ProductID` WHERE DATE(tbl_orders.order_date) = '2024-09-24' GROUP BY `tbl_orders`.`orderCode`
